    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Phylum including over 64,000 species of fungi characterized by a saclike structure, the ascus, which contains four to eight ascospores in the sexual stage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
